<p>Give Balboa or Collegiate Shag an intense start or a proper post-summer brush up. This workshop will teach you the basics of Balboa or Collegiate Shag, but the course will have a tight pace. It’s also the ideal place to wake up your Balboa or Shag basics after a summer break. To attend this workshop you should have taken some couple dance classes for to be familiar with basic terms and technique.</p>

<p>With our frequent visiting teachers Katharina and Johannes you can be sure to be in loving hands.</p>

<p>Teaching language is English and we rotate partners.</p>

<p><strong>Shag:</strong><br />
Saturday 11.00-12.30 and 13.30-15.00</p>

<p><strong>Balboa:</strong><br />
Sunday, 11.00-12.30 and 13.30-15.00</p>

